I moved from New York, after
replacing myself as CEO

00:12:18.490 --> 00:12:21.190
at Pencils of Promise,
out to the Bay Area

00:12:21.190 --> 00:12:23.290
to focus on building
a college alternative

00:12:23.290 --> 00:12:26.260
for the 21st century, really
reinventing the model of what

00:12:26.260 --> 00:12:28.060
higher education
can and should look

00:12:28.060 --> 00:12:30.290
like if you started from today.

