So our students come together
at minimum every other week.

00:17:44.580 --> 00:17:46.121
A lot of them actually
live together,

00:17:46.121 --> 00:17:49.730
because you have to live within
50 miles of your cohort city.

00:17:49.730 --> 00:17:52.062
And then finally,
