00:18:24.870 --> 00:18:27.110
real-world work experience,
either internships,

00:18:27.110 --> 00:18:29.280
fellowships, or
consulting projects,

00:18:29.280 --> 00:18:31.880
so that they can complete the
year with the actual competency

00:18:31.880 --> 00:18:35.390
