00:49:47.730 --> 00:49:53.880
is not exactly built up
for the huge population

00:49:53.880 --> 00:49:57.900
is probably going to apply
for the kind of countries

00:49:57.900 --> 00:50:00.315
in which Pencils for
Promise operates in.

00:50:00.315 --> 00:50:05.760
So do you see how technology
as a medium for instruction

00:50:05.760 --> 00:50:08.335
