00:52:10.710 --> 00:52:14.190
So maybe we can just start
younger and without any time

00:52:14.190 --> 00:52:18.062
and inject hope in
these children's eyes.

00:52:18.062 --> 00:52:18.770
ADAM BRAUN: Yeah.

00:52:18.770 --> 00:52:21.900
I think our curricular
approach certainly

00:52:21.900 --> 00:52:23.580
