00:52:27.390 --> 00:52:28.800
at the end of high school.

00:52:28.800 --> 00:52:30.960
But I think the curricular
approach certainly

00:52:30.960 --> 00:52:33.630
can be adopted by public
and private schools.

00:52:33.630 --> 00:52:35.280
The kind of product-based
and certainly

00:52:35.280 --> 00:52:37.290
the blended learning,
the technology

00:52:37.290 --> 00:52:39.702
can and should be used
in that capacity as well.

00:52:39.702 --> 00:52:42.642
AUDIENCE: And then one
