00:53:23.252 --> 00:53:25.460
gone out and become stewards
for an incredible amount

00:53:25.460 --> 00:53:27.890
of new initiatives that have
had a truly global impact.

00:53:27.890 --> 00:53:31.100
And that, for us, is absolutely
critical for long-term success.

